"    see \"Dronabinol: Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?29/40/30340?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Dronabinol: Pediatric drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
"   <br/>",
